title: 23 WAYS TO HAVE FUN AT HOME || APRIL FOOLS' DAY PRANKS
description:
Hilarious pranks for everyone at home

In this video, I show you how to make the best of April fools with these amazing prank ideas you should try. 
You can start your day by drawing a spider on the toilet paper in your bathroom. Anyone who’s terrified of spiders won’t even step in. 
You can also offer your friends some strawberries, but beforehand make sure you remove some of the fruit in the middle and fill it up with ginger or garlic.
You can also apply nail polish on a clean soap bar and put it in the bathroom. Nobody would be able to wash their hands with it. 
Another great idea is to dip Brussel sprouts in some chocolate sauce and serve them to your friend. 
You can also take an oreo cookie, remove the cream from the middle and replace it with toothpaste. 
Another fun idea is to open a bag of crisps and coat the top of it with Nutella. Then offer some crisps to your friends and watch their reaction. 

#StayAtHome

title: Munafiq - Episode 49 - 31st Mar 2020 - HAR PAL GEO
description:
Munafiq - Episode 49 - 31st Mar 2020 - HAR PAL GEO


Ujala belongs to a middle class family. When her father and brother who work for the rich business woman and politician Mrs. Sabiha meet with an unfortunate deadly factory accident, she pressurizes Ujala’s mother to compromise. As a result, despite her own reservations, Ujala agrees to marry Mrs. Sabiha’s son for the greater benefit of her struggling poor family.

Ujala’s new life in the unfamiliar surroundings of her new rich household go from bad to worse when her new husband rejects her. Will Ujala survive the constant onslaught of challenges? Will she ever be accepted and welcomed as a member of the new household? Or will she surrender to the manipulative plans of her in-laws?

LockDown पर 21 दिन बाद क्या होगा ? | Modi मंत्र को समझो, 'व्रत' से मरेगा Virus |CoronavirusOutbreak

CoronavirusOutbreak पर अब सवाल आता है कि आखिर ये व्रत 21 दिन का ही क्यों. 21 दिन (21 days) में ऐसा क्या हो जाएगा, क्या 21 दिन में Virus का खात्मा हो जाएगा. Corona को साफ करने के लिए आखिर ये 21 दिन क्यों ज़रूरी हैं.

समझिए. इस वायरस का इनक्यूबेशन पीरियड (Virus incubation period) 14 दिन (14 days) का होता है. यानी 14 दिन के अंदर कभी भी इसके संक्रमण (Infection) का पता चल सकता है. उसके बाद 5-7 दिन तक ये दूसरों को फैला सकता है. वायरस के इस लाइफ़-साइकल (Life cycle) को ब्रेक करने के लिए सरकार ने 21 दिन का फ़ैसला लिया है.
